Great Hotel
I would recommended this hotel for family travel. They have a good location and awesome top bar view. You can easily find food or convenience stores, just 2-3 minutes walking. Guest service is extremely helpful, thumbs up to Len and Thoa; I booked a shuttle bus to Hoi An and our family happy are happy with the serviced they provided. We would definitely come back!
