RMColumbus wrote a review Jan 2019
Columus26 contributions37 helpful votes
Nice Hotel With Great Views
We had a large room with a direct view of the beach. The room had a functional kitchenette and a large, modern tiled bath. The rooftop bar and pool have spectacular views. The bar has a happy hour and the cocktails are well-made and inexpensive. The breakfast is good with lots of western or Asian choices. Service was great -- one example: on a couple of occasions we ordered ice sent up to the room. Both times it arrived in under 5 minutes. We saw very few westerners there; mostly Chinese and Koreans. All in all a very nice, comfortable hotel.
Xin chao RMColumbus, It is great pleasure to learn that you had such a nice time with good impression with our service during your stay at À La Carte Da Nang Beach hotel. We are extremely happy when you found our service turned out to be kind and amazing. Especially, more than happy when we were able to meet your requirement and expectation overall. Once again, thank you so much for taking time to share us with your positive feedback. It was an honor to be at your service and we look forward to having you with us soon again for your next return to Da Nang. Sincerely, The À La Carte management team.
