Angela wrote a review Jan 2019
7 contributions4 helpful votes
good view
We can only see part of the sea from the room, since our room window is facing another building. But if you go up to the top of the hotel, there is a pool. Beautiful view up there. You can take great pictures there. The beach is just cross a street. The room was big, but the facilities are not new. There wasn't nice restaurant around, so we had dinners at the hotel. Dinner in hotel was good.
Date of stay: August 2018
Xin chao AngelaYang1, Thank you for taking the time to share your review with us. We appreciate your valuable feedback as it helps us identify the areas we can improve the guest experience. I was disappointed to learn of the shortcomings you experienced and we're currently taking steps to upgrade some of the room facilities. Sincerely, The A La Carte management
